{
  "stem": "27748.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Before we got the grades back from the final exam, we-- school had ended, and most of us had left.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So at the time after the mock examination, there was some sort of planning of what we were going to do next.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the headmistress, I remember to this day saying, I didn't know you were so poor.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I've never forgiven her for that one.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so anyway, in this same category, I later made-- but I didn't know how to study.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't study, and so on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But then I was shaken up enough to study after that first grade came up.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But, anyway, her notion then was I should become a watchmaker.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and that has also stayed with me, because I became an academician who wrote books later, and so on.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But something inside of me has always yearned to do something with my hands, and that, perhaps, being a watchmaker would have been a better idea.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK, so she was a lady who was a very strong, powerful person, a very big, physically, very huge woman.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At least from my point of view, she was huge.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe in actuality, if I had met her again, she might have shrunk.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But she was huge.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anna Essinger, I mentioned her before, I think.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So, anyway, she was a very enterprising, strong, powerful woman, who was to the public, this big savior of children.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she went around the country raising money for the schools to keep body and soul together, because it was a private school.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she ran it, and got the life blood for it in the form of funds that she solicited.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So she had this reputation of being this very powerful, humane person.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I saw of her with utter dread.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
